      "id": "PopularPost59677",
      "post_content": "Dwarven Weaponsmith has an extremely weak ability. It allows you to turn your artifacts into +1/+1 counters. If it worked at instant speed, this would be a decent (if limited) ability. But since you must do it during your upkeep, you can't use it as a combat trick, or to sac an artifact that was all ready headed to the graveyard. There are few artifacts that you'd ever want to sacrifice to the dwarves. Perhaps this could be used effectively in conjunction with [The Hive](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Hive), or it might be a good way to get rid of a pesky [Mishra's War Machine](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's War Machine). With all that said, the Weaponsmith is a 1/1 with an ability for 2 mana, so not completely unplayable.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost59677\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Dwarven Weaponsmith has an extremely weak ability.  It allows you to turn your artifacts into +1/+1 counters.  If it worked at instant speed, this would be a decent (if limited) ability.  But since you must do it during your upkeep, you can't use it as a combat trick, or to sac an artifact that was all ready headed to the graveyard.  There are few artifacts that you'd ever want to sacrifice to the dwarves.  Perhaps this could be used effectively in conjunction with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"The Hive\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Hive\">The Hive</a>, or it might be a good way to get rid of a pesky <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mishra's War Machine\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's War Machine\">Mishra's War Machine</a>.  With all that said, the Weaponsmith is a 1/1 with an ability for 2 mana, so not completely unplayable.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '59677'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (3/12/2010 11:42:25 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n      